"""
VRPTW RL v12

Changes from v11:
- DDQN controls ALL non-default mode decisions (post_imp_lock and route_reduce hardcodes removed)
- _segment_reward: direct NV penalty removed; potential shaping carries NV signal
- Mode bandits: ALL bandits decay each segment (not just the active one)
- Operator weights: per-mode dw/rw arrays (shape [n_modes, N_D/N_R])
- EliteArchive: top-k plans per instance; warm-starts subsequent runs
- OR-Tools GLS baseline (ALGO_ORTOOLS)
- Cross-instance RC2 transfer (ALGO_HYBRID_DDQN_TRANSFER_RC2)
- Checkpoint resume in run_benchmark (skip already-computed combos on restart)
- Wall-clock kill switch (max_wall_hours) in run_benchmark
- smoke_test no longer accepts production CFG from __main__
- Config: n_runs=3, iterations trimmed for 12h Kaggle session,
  post_improve_intensify_segments removed
"""

